    "This part of the analysis delved into the educators' perceptions regarding their knowledge of ADWTs, the opportunities and risks in utilizing ADWTs in teaching and research, and what they think should be done to use these tools ethically and effectively.",
    "First, we present the results of the survey questionnaire in a Likert-scale response format.",
    "Table 1 shows the frequency counts, means, and standard deviations of the educators' responses to the perception questions with a five-point Likert-scale response format.",
    "Items 1-3 measure the educators' knowledge, skills, and intentions in using the AI tools in question.",
    "Their mean values of 2.87, 2.60, and 3.13 fall in the neutral range, and their respective standard deviations of 1.34, 1.31, and 1.29 indicate a low level of variability."
